These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, white
There 2 different types of food: lime, pineapple
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, satire
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person eating lime is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | white       | lavender |
| Food         | pineapple | lime  |
| Movie-Genre       | satire    | musical    |
| Beverage   | 7up       | iced-tea      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, d&b
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, emerald
2 different games are played: scrabble, whist
There 2 different types of food: onion, lime
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | d&b     | reggae |
| Color           | chestnut | emerald      |
| Game   | whist  | scrabble      |
| Food         | onion | lime     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, emerald
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, fishing
2 different games are played: monopoly, whist
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes blue is the person playing whist##1
3. the game-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Color      | blue | emerald  |
| Cigar          | game    | tiparillo   |
| Hobby   | fishing  | video-games   |
| Game     | whist     | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, baseball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Color      | purple       | light-blue |
| Sport          | baseball         | golf    |
| Flower           | daffodil | tulip    |
| Hobby   | sudoku           | fishing   |

