1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| City   | marseilles         | london    |
| Cigar       | tiparillo     | game  |
