There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
2 different games are played: poker, billiard
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter
1. the person playing billiard is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Birthday          | july | october |
| Beverage   | milk     | hot-chocolate      |
| Game   | poker | billiard    |
| Transport           | jet-ski    | scooter    |

