.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, grey
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, cooking
City: boston, marseilles
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Color           | grey | purple     |
| Flower   | daisy          | orchid |
| Hobby           | fishing          | cooking    |
| City     | marseilles            | boston       |

 